### Healthcheck
GET {{host}}/health

### Métriques Prometheus
GET {{host}}/metrics

### Inscription
# @name register
POST {{host}}/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "omar@ynov.com", "password": "S3curePass!" }

### Connexion
# @name login
POST {{host}}/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "omar@ynov.com", "password": "S3curePass!" }

### Signaler une place libre (+10 pts)
POST {{host}}/v1/reports
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}

{ "type": "free", "lat": 45.4397, "lng": 4.3872 }

### Places et parkings à proximité
GET {{host}}/v1/spots?lat=45.4397&lng=4.3872&radius=2000

### Prédiction IA
GET {{host}}/v1/predictions?lat=45.4397&lng=4.3872

### Parkings mondiaux + voirie (OSM — nécessite internet)
GET {{host}}/v1/osm/parkings?lat=48.8583&lng=2.3736&radius=1500

### Route protégée sans token → 401 attendu
POST {{host}}/v1/reports
Content-Type: application/json

{ "type": "free", "lat": 45.44, "lng": 4.39 }
